                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <persName>Belton, Bell Co.</persName>\n                <placeName>Texas</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Feby 17th 1866</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Many years have<lb/> elapsed since I had the pleasure<lb/> of\n                addressing you, and now do<lb/> so to ascertain whether you<lb/> are still\n                publishing your Portu-<lb/>guese Hebrew &amp; English Prayer Books<lb/> and\n                Pentateuchâ€”together with a<lb/> Jewish version of the Bible in<lb/> English, and if\n                yea, you will<lb/> please send me a <sic>catalogue</sic>\n                <lb/> of prices of the same.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You will also inform me<lb/> how I am to get the money (if<lb/> I\n                should order any of the books)<lb/> to you. When I hear from<lb/> you will inform\n                how<lb/> to forward to me such</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p36m33k9d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
